sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Wallet
    participant Arbiscan as Arbiscan (Arbitrum)
    participant Contract as NyxoraAgentRegistry
    participant Gateway as Nyxora Local Gateway
    participant Web3 as Web3 Network (e.g. Ethereum)

    Note over User, Web3: Normal Registration Flow
    User->>Contract: registerAgent("My Agent")
    Contract-->>User: Success (isActive = true)
    
    Note over User, Web3: Normal Transaction Flow
    Gateway->>Contract: checkRegistryStatus()
    Contract-->>Gateway: isActive = true
    Gateway->>Web3: Execute transaction
    Web3-->>Gateway: Success

    Note over User, Web3: Emergency Kill-Switch Flow
    User->>Arbiscan: Connect Wallet (Mobile/Safe Device)
    Arbiscan->>Contract: toggleAgentStatus(false)
    Contract-->>Arbiscan: Success (isActive = false)
    
    Gateway->>Contract: checkRegistryStatus()
    Contract-->>Gateway: isActive = false
    Gateway--xWeb3: Transaction Blocked (403)
